address.streetAddress: The Aurora Plan, Sendero at Pioneer Meadows

location.fullValue: The Aurora Plan, Sendero at Pioneer Meadows

data.description: Beautiful, hard to find one story home. This 1874 sq. ft, beauty offers a spacious great room layout with a cozy fireplace and has 3 bedrooms plus a den/study and a 3-car garage. The kitchen features custom granite counters, gas cooking, an island, a large walk-in pantry and a breakfast bar. There is a laundry room with built-in cabinets.  The lovely back yard has a covered patio and is fully landscaped. Shopping, golf, and walking trails are nearby. Seller is the original owner. Refrigerator, washer and dryer included at no value and with no warranty.
